@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Inicio";
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="~/android-chrome-512x512.jpg" />

    <title>Nexeron ERP - Sistema de Gestión Centralizado</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Nexeron ERP: La solución integral en la nube para optimizar los procesos de tu gran negocio o PYME." />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        /* --- EFECTO DE DESPLAZAMIENTO SUAVE --- */
        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        :root {
            --primary-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #5a189a, #9d4edd);
            --primary-color: #7b2cbf;
            --primary-hover: #3c096c;
            --bg-color: #f8f7fa;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --text-dark: #240046;
            --text-muted: #6b6375;
            --transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* --- HEADER & NAV --- */
        header {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(157, 78, 221, 0.1);
        }

        nav {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }

        .logo {
            height: 40px;
            width: auto;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        /* --- BOTONES CON ESQUINAS REDONDEADAS --- */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: var(--transition);
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .btn--primary {
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(123, 44, 191, 0.2);
            border: none;
        }

        .btn--primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(123, 44, 191, 0.3);
        }

        .btn--outline {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            border: 2px solid rgba(123, 44, 191, 0.4);
        }

        .btn--outline:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary-color);
            background-color: rgba(123, 44, 191, 0.05);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* --- HERO SECTION --- */
        .hero {
            padding: 11rem 2rem 6rem 2rem;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(157, 78, 221, 0.08), transparent 50%),
                              radial-gradient(circle at bottom left, rgba(90, 24, 154, 0.04), transparent 50%);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.2rem;
        }

        /* --- ESTILOS ICONOS SVG --- */
        .feature-icon {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            display: block;
        }

        /* --- MÓDULOS DEL ERP --- */
        .features {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 4rem 2rem 8rem 2rem;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .grid-features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(157, 78, 221, 0.08);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(90, 24, 154, 0.02);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: rgba(157, 78, 221, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(90, 24, 154, 0.06);
        }

        .card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* --- FOOTER --- */
        footer {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(157, 78, 221, 0.1);
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        @@media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-links { display: none; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.4rem; }
            .hero h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; }
            .hero-buttons { flex-direction: column; width: 100%; }
            .btn { width: 100%; text-align: center; }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <nav>
            <a href="#" class="logo-container">
                <img class="logo" src="~/Nexeron.png" alt="Logo Nexeron">
                <span>Nexeron</span>
            </a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#caracteristicas">Módulos</a></li>
                <li><a href="@Url.Action("Login", "Home")" class="btn btn--outline" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;">Iniciar Sesión</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>ERP Cloud Inteligente</h1>
                <h2>La solución digital centralizada para gestionar y llevar el control total de tu negocio.<br><strong>¿Tienes dudas o necesitas soporte técnico?</strong> Solicita información directa a nuestro equipo.</h2>

                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="@Url.Action("Login", "Home")" class="btn btn--primary">Acceder al ERP</a>
                    <a href="mailto:nexeronprog@gmail.com?subject=Soporte%20e%20Informacion%20-%20Nexeron%20ERP" class="btn btn--outline">Solicitar Información</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="features" id="caracteristicas">
            <h2 class="section-title">Todo tu negocio conectado en una sola plataforma</h2>

            <div class="grid-features">
                <div class="card">
                    <svg class="feature-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"></line><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"></line><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"></line></svg>
                    <h3>Finanzas y Contabilidad</h3>
                    <p>Control de tesorería, balances automatizados y flujos de caja en tiempo real bajo normativas vigentes.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <svg class="feature-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
                    <h3>Gestión Comercial & CRM</h3>
                    <p>Optimiza el ciclo de ventas, haz seguimiento de clientes potenciales y cierra presupuestos ágilmente.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <svg class="feature-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 16 12 14 15 10 15 8 12 2 12"></polyline><path d="M5.45 5.11L2 12v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-6l-3.45-6.89A2 2 0 0 0 16.76 4H7.24a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11z"></path></svg>
                    <h3>Logística y Stock</h3>
                    <p>Administra almacenes múltiples, inventarios inteligentes y compras eficientes a proveedores.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <svg class="feature-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 1 1-2.83 2.83l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 1 1-2.83-2.83l.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33-1.82 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1 0-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 1 1 2.83-2.83l.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82.33H9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 4 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 1 1 2.83 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 0 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"></path></svg>
                    <h3>Producción y Procesos</h3>
                    <p>Planifica cadenas de fabricación, monitoriza costes operativos y optimiza los tiempos de entrega.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Nexeron ERP</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>